=== Debian/Ubuntu/Mint ===

1. Install build dependecies
	sudo apt-get install build-essential libqtgstreamer-dev libgstreamer-plugins-base0.10-dev libdcmtk2-dev libwrap0-dev libssl-dev

2. Make Makefile:
	qmake CONFIG+=dicom beryllium.pro

- or -
	qmake CONFIG+=debug CONFIG+=declarative_debug CONFIG+=dicom beryllium.pro

for debug.

3. Make Beryllium:
	make

=== Suse/Fedora/RedHat ===

1. Install build dependecies
	sudo yum install qt-devel qt-gstreamer-devel dcmtk-devel openssl-devel

2. Make Makefile:

replace line
    LIBS += -ldcmnet -lwrap -li2d -ldcmdata -ldcmtls -loflog -lofstd -lssl
with line
    LIBS += -L/usr/lib/dcmtk -ldcmnet -llibi2d -ldcmdata -ldcmtls -loflog -lofstd -lssl

(there is fedora.patch for that)

	qmake-qt4 CONFIG+=dicom beryllium.pro

- or -
	qmake-qt4 CONFIG+=debug CONFIG+=declarative_debug CONFIG+=dicom beryllium.pro

for debug.

3. Make Beryllium:
	make

